By Joseph P
This is an excellent compilation of songs that kept Dean in our hearts and in our thoughts. These are the songs that most everyone will associate Dean Martin with. When Dean's name is brought into a conversation you immediately start to hum to yourself songs like "That's Amore", "Memories Are Made of This", "Return To Me", and the unfogetable "Volare". If you remember one or two of these tunes, and I'm very sure you, maybe even more, this compilation is the one to get. It'll even give you a taste of some of the classic Italian songs Dean recorded during his career. He just always seemed so relaxed whether he was singing or acting. I've been a very big fan of Deans' for years and a very big record collector as well and this compilation is now part of my collection.
